HEADWORD: Potlid
<hw>Pot"lid`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The lid or cover of a
pot.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Potlid valve</b></col>, <cd>a valve covering a round hole
